[{"Code":"en","Title":"Industry Specific Requirement","Slug":"draft","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote data-block-id=\"mb3o6q5c-l1l8hp-010\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\" style=\"background:rgb(221, 247, 255);border-left:4px solid rgb(0, 106, 138);overflow:auto;\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6ssn-rbk6cu-013\">Note:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-j91f7e-014\"><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-iun9tk-015\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-w7qg79-016\">Please select a country from the list provided to filter the industries that have additional requirements within that specific country.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">If an industry is not specifically listed below, it generally means that no specific requirement is needed.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">To easily locate what you're looking for, please use the search button. 🔎</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appHTKmJLagJ6vqw2/shrSTa1mJSY3x1rdA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\" class=\"airtable-embed\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"mb3o7q75-knsnoz-020\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Industry Specific Requirement","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Persyaratan Spesifik Industri","Slug":"draft","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mb3o6q5c-l1l8hp-010\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6ssn-rbk6cu-013\">Catatan:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-j91f7e-014\"><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-iun9tk-015\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-w7qg79-016\">Silakan pilih negara dari daftar yang tersedia untuk memfilter industri yang memiliki persyaratan tambahan di negara tersebut.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">Jika suatu industri tidak tercantum secara spesifik di bawah ini, umumnya berarti tidak ada persyaratan khusus yang diperlukan.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">Untuk menemukan apa yang Anda cari dengan mudah, silakan gunakan tombol pencarian. &#x1f50e;</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appHTKmJLagJ6vqw2/shrSTa1mJSY3x1rdA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"mb3o7q75-knsnoz-020\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Persyaratan Spesifik Industri","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ข้อกำหนดเฉพาะสำหรับอุตสาหกรรม","Slug":"draft","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mb3o6q5c-l1l8hp-010\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6ssn-rbk6cu-013\">หมายเหตุ:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-j91f7e-014\"><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-iun9tk-015\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-w7qg79-016\">โปรดเลือกประเทศจากรายการที่ให้ไว้เพื่อกรองอุตสาหกรรมที่มีข้อกำหนดเพิ่มเติมภายในประเทศนั้นๆ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">หากอุตสาหกรรมใดไม่ได้ระบุไว้โดยเฉพาะด้านล่างนี้ โดยทั่วไปหมายความว่าไม่จำเป็นต้องมีข้อกำหนดเฉพาะใดๆ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">เพื่อให้ค้นหาสิ่งที่คุณต้องการได้ง่ายขึ้น โปรดใช้ปุ่มค้นหา &#x1f50e;</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appHTKmJLagJ6vqw2/shrSTa1mJSY3x1rdA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"mb3o7q75-knsnoz-020\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ข้อกำหนดเฉพาะสำหรับอุตสาหกรรม","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Requisito Específico de la Industria","Slug":"draft","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mb3o6q5c-l1l8hp-010\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6ssn-rbk6cu-013\">Nota:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-j91f7e-014\"><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvj-iun9tk-015\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-w7qg79-016\">Por favor, seleccione un país de la lista proporcionada para filtrar las industrias que tienen requisitos adicionales dentro de ese país específico.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">Si una industria no está específicamente listada a continuación, generalmente significa que no se necesita ningún requisito específico.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-ev1cor-017\"><p data-block-id=\"mb3o6zvk-z4zuz0-018\">Para localizar fácilmente lo que está buscando, por favor, use el botón de búsqueda. &#x1f50e;</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appHTKmJLagJ6vqw2/shrSTa1mJSY3x1rdA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"mb3o7q75-knsnoz-020\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Requisito Específico de la Industria","Description":null}]